Package: workspace
Title: Project-Aware Paths and 'targets' Pipelines in a Workspace
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bangou", "Zheng", , "zheng.bangyou@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides helpers to work with multi-project directory layouts marked by
    '.workspace' and '.project' files. Includes utilities to resolve project-aware
    file paths and wrappers to run and read '{targets}' pipelines per project.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    rprojroot
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rstudioapi,
    targets,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://workspace.bangyou.me/,
    https://github.com/byzheng/workspace
